### from(unlock_blocks): [UnlockBlocks](#unlockblocks)

| Parameter     | Type                          | Description |
| ------------- | ----------------------------- | ----------- |
| unlock_blocks | [UnlockBlock[]](#unlockblock) |             |

### get(index): Optional&lt;[UnlockBlock](#unlockblock)&gt;

Gets a clone of an `UnlockBlock` from `UnlockBlocks`.
Returns the referenced unlock block if the requested unlock block was a reference.

| Parameter | Type | Description |
| --------- | ---- | ----------- |
| index     | long |             |
